MGM Grand Inde yarn sey di matter don file registration form wit di Securities and Exchange Commission for one public offering wey be six million common share.

Beverly Hills, California based company don yarn sey e go get 26.9 million common shares after di auction.

Hotel and gaming company talk sey Merrill Lynch Capital Markets go dey lead di underwriters.

Dem go use dis money wey de sell take do renovation, and refurbishing projects, plus di planned MGM Grand Hotel, Kasino, and theme park.

